jun piẍ pergamino otoq tz´ok tka´yin Harry t-xi t-xo´n toj t-mes. “Ma b´ant wu´ne
ma tz´ok nq´o´ne aju´ u´j extzen aye n-chi ayon kyi´j n-chi ayon. . . . Oh, q´onxa amb´il weye tun n-b´inchene
jalin. . . .»
“B´a´nxix, Argus,” chi xu´j. “Aqeye kab´e,” chi xu´j, n-chi tka´yin tjaq´
toj Fred ex George, «chʼix tel kynikʼ tiʼj tiʼ in bʼaj kyiʼj qeju in che bʼinchan nya bʼaʼn
toj n-xnaq´tzb´ile.
¿b´i´n tza´n? chi Fred. “Mya n-ximane qa aqo´ye.”
Xi t-xko´n twitz t-xu´jil.
Tqʼama Fred jlu: «George, in kubʼ nximane qa ma qo chʼiy twitzju xnaqʼtzbʼil in xi qʼet toj tkyaqil ambʼil».
“Ax tok, ax ikx weye n-chi b´isune ikyjo,” chi George tuk´e t-xilen.
