ky-b´e kyxol tze´ jalin, ky-xik´ ky-xik´ tz´u´m n-chi b´et
t-xilen ky-xmilal, ky-witz n-chi qoptz´aj toj qlolj. A
myia jun t-xilen jalin. . . .
“b´a´n,” chij tuk´a tq´oj, “jyonxa jun extzen jaxa, yajxi´tl.”

